Monetta Fund
Young Investor Fund
Scholar's Edge®529













Monetta offers two mutual funds. The Monetta Fund actively invests in large-cap growth companies. The Young Investor Fund combines passive/active large-cap growth investing.
The Monetta Young Investor Fund (YIF) is also available as an option on the Scholar's Edge® 529 College Savings Plan!









Young Investor Fund 

The Monetta Young Investor Fund seeks long-term capital growth, by combining a passive and active investment approach.
Learn More













 YIF 529 Option

You  can receive all the benefits of the Monetta Young Investor Fund as you save for your  child’s 529 college education.
Learn More












Monetta Fund

The Monetta Fund seeks long-term capital growth by primarily investing in large-capitalization growth stocks.
