Company Overview of Monetta Financial Services, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Monetta Financial Services, Inc. is an employee owned investment manager. The firm provides its services to investment companies. It launches and manages equity, fixed income, and balanced mutual funds for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity and fixed income markets of the United States. Monetta Financial Services, Inc. was founded in 1975 and is based in Wheaton, Illinois.


